ed="T" n="0863b09"/><persName key="A013540">釋法朗</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000009928">姑蘇</placeName>人也。稟質溫潤，約心堅確，誦<lb
ed="T" n="0863b10"/>《觀音明呪》，神効屢彰。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京闕</ref>觀光，人皆知重。<date key="j19628781963261" notAfter-iso="+0663-02-15" notBefore-iso="+0662-01-28"><name>龍<lb
ed="T" n="0863b11"/>朔</name>二年</date>，<persName key="A013543">城陽公主</persName>有疾沈篤，尚藥供治，無所<lb
ed="T" n="0863b12"/>不至。<ref type="person" target="#A013543">公主</ref>乃<persName key="A002146">高宗<roleName>大帝</roleName></persName>同母妹也──友愛殊<lb
ed="T" n="0863b13"/>厚──，降<persName key="A006422">杜如晦</persName>子<persName key="A013541">荷</persName>。<persName key="A013541">荷</persName>死，再行<persName key="A013542">薛瓘</persName>。既疾綿<lb
ed="T" n="0863b14"/>困，有告，言<persName key="A013540">朗</persName>能持祕呪，理病多瘳。及召<persName key="A013540">朗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0863b15"/>至，設壇持誦，信宿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g499"/>而安，賞賚豐渥。其錢帛<lb
ed="T" n="0863b16"/>珍寶，<persName key="A013540">朗</persName>迴為對面施。<ref type="person" target="#A013543">公主</ref>奏請改寺額曰<lb
ed="T" n="0863b17"/><placeName key="PL000000042420">觀音寺</placeName>，以居之。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042420">此寺</ref>本<placeName key="PL000000042420"><placeName>隋</placeName><placeName>靈感寺</placeName></placeName>，<date key="j19340271934410" notAfter-iso="+0584-02-18" notBefore-iso="+0583-01-31"><name>開皇</name>三年</date><lb
ed="T" n="0863b18"/>置<ptr target="#n2988"/>。<persName key="A004324">文帝</persName>移都，多掘城中陵園塚墓，徒葬郊<lb
ed="T" n="0863b19"/>野，而置<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042420">此寺</ref>。至<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName><date key="j19479061948289" notAfter-iso="+0622-02-18" notBefore-iso="+0621-01-31"><name>武德</name>四年</date>廢，至此更題<lb
ed="T" n="0863b20"/>額。<persName key="A013540">朗</persName>尋終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042420">此寺</ref>焉。</p>
